  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, again, run and look for something and carry whatever you were able to carry and settle down again and start from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At first, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I mean, they were not-- working [INAUDIBLE], the slave labor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That came a little bit later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So at first, I don't recall this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were people-- rather, I remember the selections and transports of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the ones that were destined to work, the work wasn't immediate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was in the process of organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, in the ghetto, in the very beginning, they tried to organize sort of schools, if that was possible, or orphanages or some workshop, some different kinds of studies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's, you know, hard to imagine mentioning about it because the life, itself, in the ghetto was misery.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's hunger, epidemic of typhoid fever, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people dying on the streets, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] complete deterioration of life from day to day.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it's hard to imagine that still there were a lot of efforts which were, unfortunately, useless.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
